pageContext.claim: “This is about a 5,500-seat arena and I said to my people, ‘Why so small?’”
pageContext.analysis: Kellogg Arena seats up to 6,200, according to its website. Local officials said Trump filled the venue with approximately 5,400 attendees. The arena holds nearly 5,200 people and an extra 1,000 when risers are set up on the north end.
